org.svvrl.goal.core.layout

Class Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.svvrl.goal.core.layout.Edge

  • public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used for edges of a graph. An edge may be directed or undirected but the edge itself does not know. Two edges are equal if they have the same source node and the same destination node.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
